### 用户登录获取JWT Token
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 发送消息（新话题）
POST http://localhost:3000/chat/send
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "你好，我想了解一下人工智能的发展历史"
}

### 发送消息（继续当前话题）
POST http://localhost:3000/chat/send
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "能详细说说深度学习的发展吗？",
  "topicId": 1
}

### 获取话题列表
GET http://localhost:3000/chat/topics
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 获取话题消息
GET http://localhost:3000/chat/topics/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 归档话题
PUT http://localhost:3000/chat/topics/1/archive
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}} 